videos.headline: Melrose doesn't see a suspension coming for Boyle
videos.description: Barry Melrose disagrees with Islanders coach Jack Capuano, who says Lightning center Brian Boyle should be suspended for his overtime hit on Thomas Hickey. Melrose didn't see a hit to the head, while Capuano thought it was.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Melrose doesn't see a suspension coming for Boyle) 2016/05/03 SC
